{"tid":18857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滅鼠奇招 美國紐約這麼做！","createTime":"2016-12-02T13:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T14:04:26.000Z","uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23697a70c26384511ff698a9b5e7b09bfdce6b03","tid":18857,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"根據美國《NBC》報導，美國紐約的公園內鼠患問題日益嚴重，許多老鼠光天化日成群結隊盤據路旁，影響衛生及年幼遊客安全。<br />\n<br />\n對此，紐約市衛生部門週二表示，他們已於曼哈頓上城的「J. Hood Wright Park」公園測試一實驗性的滅鼠方法，投置乾冰於鼠窩附近，乾冰於常溫中急速蒸發會產生高濃度的二氧化碳，讓老鼠窒息死去。衛生官員宣稱此為人道滅絕，老鼠不會感到痛苦，也不會影響到其他野生動物及人類。<br />\n<br />\n不過該衛生部門隨後也指出，該滅鼠方式不適用於建築物內或其他以水泥建造的場所。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1776097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1776097&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=fcb395ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1776097&h=fc0a8240\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1776097</a>"},{"pid":"01b98f1d07e25f7851de94c07fd91a5d48eff4c2","tid":18857,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"封少一個窿即刻全部衝曬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6918c240680d7b226fa1e6d3ee870a01edf7b2aa","tid":18857,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"諗起呢段<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=eM2RTw-vp78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeM2RTw-vp78&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=c99f1432\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=eM2RTw-vp78</a>"},{"pid":"a31c86c41d33a5ae27ef21f57145fd61d6c25f0d","tid":18857,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=